Class MetaDataDependentObject

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable

    public class MetaDataDependentObject
extends MetaDataTable
    Represents properties of a dependent object from the Siperian repository. It derives all of its properties from the superclass and is in place only for applying a specific type to dependent objects.
    See Also:
    DescribeSiperianObjectRequest, Serialized Form
